    • exports

      ModuleBuilder exports(String packageName, List<String> toModules, Mod... modifiers)
      Adds exports directive.
      Parameters:
      packageName - name of the package this module opens.
      toModules - names of the modules access to the package is open to. If empty, access is open to all modules.
      modifiers - either Mod.MANDATED or Mod.SYNTHETIC may be given.
      Returns:
      this builder.
